1. Update linux using cmd
    sudo apt update && sudo apt dist-upgrade -y

2. Install pip and some other packages which is prerequsit for Ansible using below command 
    sudo apt install -y libssl-dev libffi-dev python-dev python3-pip

3. Install Ansible and azure suit 
    sudo pip install ansible[azure]

4. Craete a Directory 
    mkdir ~/.azure

5. Create a Credentials the above folder
    nano ~/.azure/credentails